{
  "text": "Diesel generators are used to supply peak load on the Diesel (100%) configuration system and when SOC is low for battery charging on PV (100%) and the combined PV + Diesel configuration system. Capacity of diesel generator is determined using equation (2) . [CITATION_1] ",
